    - Each inst. that can R/W, will do so respecting the hierarchy.

      16 KiBs #l-m-meta[(L1)] $subset.eq$ 256 KiBs #l-m-meta[(L2)] $subset.eq$ 2 MiBs #l-m-meta[(L3)]
